Document: RemoteTransform3D
Path: godot/classes/class_remotetransform3d.rst
Summary: Describes the force_update_cache method and its purpose in the RemoteTransform3D class.

Method: force_update_cache() → void
Forces an immediate update of the transform cache, ensuring all connected nodes reflect the latest transformation data. This is typically used when manual synchronization of spatial relationships is required between remote nodes.
